{{vgname2|2016年波士頓特級錦標賽|en=Boston Major 2016}}也被稱為秋季賽，是一項[[電子遊戲|電子遊戲]]《[[Dota_2|Dota 2]]》的[[電子競技|電子競技]]比賽。本賽事是[[威尔乌|威尔乌]]舉辦的《Dota 2》四大聯賽的其中一站。本屆賽事於2016年12月7日至12月10日在美國[[波士頓|波士頓]]內的{{link-en|Wang Theatre|Wang Theatre}}舉行，總獎金為3百萬美金<ref name="Boston Major">{{cite web|url=http://www.thebostonmajor.com/|title=THE BOSTON MAJOR|work=PGL|date=2016-12-07|accessdate=2016-12-11|archive-date=2016-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161221055136/http://www.thebostonmajor.com/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。本次賽事以之前的特錦賽不同，波士頓特錦賽是是首次以[[單敗淘汰制|單敗淘汰制]]來進行比賽<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.redbull.com/us/en/esports/stories/1331827201662/dota-2-s-best-of-one-series-is-valve-trying-new-things|title=Dota 2 Wants to Avoid the 'World Series Problem'|work=Red Bull|date=2016-11-02|accessdate=2016-12-11|archive-date=2016-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161111061956/http://www.redbull.com/us/en/esports/stories/1331827201662/dota-2-s-best-of-one-series-is-valve-trying-new-things|dead-url=no}}</ref>。最終，OG以3-1的成績擊敗來自希臘的Ad Finem隊伍並且是續上一屆[[2016年馬尼拉特級錦標賽|馬尼拉特級錦標賽]]後第三次奪得特錦賽冠軍<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.espn.com/esports/story/_/id/18251669/2016-dota-2-boston-major-og-defeats-ad-finem-third-major-title|title=OG defeats Ad Finem at Boston Major for its third Major title|work=ESPN|date=2016-12-11|accessdate=2016-12-11|archive-date=2016-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161211210531/http://www.espn.com/esports/story/_/id/18251669/2016-dota-2-boston-major-og-defeats-ad-finem-third-major-title|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

